These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  security-guard, analyst
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, zombie
There are 2 different nationalities: german, malaysian
2 different pets are kept: lizard, horse
The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, taxi
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
2. the analyst is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the owner of the lizard is the malaysian##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the horse is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | 7up       |
| Hobby         | traveling   | rock-climbing     |
| Job           | security-guard | analyst   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie   | documentary  |
| Nationality   | malaysian | german |
| Pet           | lizard      | horse     |
| Transport     | taxi    | trike   |

