.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, 7up
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, filmmaking
The people have 2 different jobs:  electrician, photographer
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: salsa, house
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, canadian
2 different pets are kept: horse, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, skateboard
1. the photographer is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the owner of the cat is the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
4. the canadian is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | 7up |
| Hobby         | filmmaking        | camping  |
| Job           | electrician | photographer  |
| Music-Genre   | house            | salsa    |
| Nationality   | dutch     | canadian   |
| Pet           | horse         | cat    |
| Transport     | jet-ski           | skateboard      |

