.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: lime, pear
The people have 2 different jobs:  scientist, police-officer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: time-travel, mystery
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, snake
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: snowboarding, lacrosse
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, ship
1. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
3. the person eating lime is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
4. the scientist is on the right of the person driving the boat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Beverage      | almond-milk          | sprite       |
| Food          | pear   | lime   |
| Job           | police-officer   | scientist     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | mystery        |
| Pet           | guinea-pig      | snake       |
| Sport         | snowboarding       | lacrosse |
| Transport     | boat          | ship |

